ature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>此外，我们已经在Pekora Usada的分销中宣布了该产品，并且我们计划确定精酿可乐的独特口味。我实际上把它与咖喱可乐和超辣可乐等各种东西分开并品尝了。</p><p>点击此处进行产品预订。<br /> <a href="https://www.u-products.co.jp/view/page/usadapekora" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.u-products.co.jp/view/page/usadapekora</a></p><h2>产品详情</h2><h3>Usada Pekora 原创可乐糖浆“Pecola” 200ml x 2 瓶</h3><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/08/pastedimage0-be422a49e37c4eb7922a711bfa7d2f59-kix.g034nr92q58a.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/08/pastedimage0-be422a49e37c4eb7922a711bfa7d2f59-kix.g034nr92q58a-1024x683.png"></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/08/pastedimage0-be422a49e37c4eb7922a711bfa7d2f59-kix.15xjc0sz8r8n.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/08/pastedimage0-be422a49e37c4eb7922a711bfa7d2f59-kix.15xjc0sz8r8n-1024x683.png"></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/08/pastedimage0-be422a49e37c4eb7922a711bfa7d2f59-kix.3qpvvgvkfaf4.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/08/pastedimage0-be422a49e37c4eb7922a711bfa7d2f59-kix.3qpvvgvkfaf4-1024x683.png"></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/08/pastedimage0-be422a49e37c4eb7922a711bfa7d2f59-kix.3asyrq6b40mi.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/08/pastedimage0-be422a49e37c4eb7922a711bfa7d2f59-kix.3asyrq6b40mi-1024x683.png"></a></p><table><tbody><tr><td>产品名称</td><td>Usada Pekora 原创可乐糖浆“Pecola” 200ml x 2 瓶</td></tr><tr><td>内容</td><td>原包装可乐糖浆200ml*2瓶</td></tr><tr><td>稀释比例</td><td>4-5次</td></tr><tr><td>价格</td><td>5,400日元（含税）</td></tr><tr><td>发布日期</td><td>2023 年 10 月下旬</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>“佩科